                                        <p>Avow Apparel will gladly accept returns on items purchased at regular price. The original tags must be attached &amp; the item(s) must be in new condition (item(s) may not be washed, worn, or altered in any way). All returns must be received in our warehouse within 25 days from the date you placed your order. All reduced price merchandise is final sale and no refunds/exchanges will be granted towards such items. Merchandise purchased using promotional coupons are eligible for returns. All items purchased at in-person events such as pop up shops, trade shows, etc. are not eligible for returns.</p>
                                        <p>Please allow 2-3 weeks for your return to be received and processed. Most returns are processed within 7 days of receipt in our warehouse. As soon as your return is processed you will receive a confirmation email. A refund will be issued (excluding all shipping costs) to the original form of payment. Remember, every financial institution has it's own processing times and funds will be made available accordingly. </p>
                                        <p>
                                            Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer except in cases of product defect or error on the part of Avow Apparel (for example if incorrect product(s) was shipped.) In such cases, Avow Apparel will pay for the cost of return shipping as well as the cost of shipping the correct or non-defective product(s) out to you. As stated in our Return &amp; Exchange Policy, all reduced price merchandise &amp; merchandise purchased at in-person events such as pop up shops, trade shows, etc. are final sale and no refunds/exchanges will be granted towards such items. In cases of product defect or error on the of Avow Apparel, you may return reduced price merchandise and merchandise purchased at in-person events for a full refund. If, in such cases, you would like the order to be replaced with the correct item/non-defective item of the same style/colour/size as indicated on the original order, this will be subject to availability and Avow Apparel cannot guarantee that the product(s) will be in stock at the time the return is processed. In cases of product defect or error on the part of Avow Apparel, a new item will be shipped to the customer, using the same shipping method as on the original order, within 3 business days (provided that the item is still available in our inventory) and shipping costs will be paid for by Avow Apparel. If you receive a defective product or the incorrect item(s) was shipped to you please contact us at <a href="mailto:Info@AvowApparel.com">Info@AvowApparel.com<script cf-hash="f9e31" type="text/javascript">
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           /* <![CDATA[ */!function () { try { var t = "currentScript" in document ? document.currentScript : function () { for (var t = document.getElementsByTagName("script"), e = t.length; e--;) if (t[e].getAttribute("cf-hash")) return t[e] }(); if (t && t.previousSibling) { var e, r, n, i, c = t.previousSibling, a = c.getAttribute("data-cfemail"); if (a) { for (e = "", r = parseInt(a.substr(0, 2), 16), n = 2; a.length - n; n += 2) i = parse