                                        </p>
                                        <p>In order to exchange a product(s) you simply return the merchandise and place a new order. New orders can be placed at any time and you do not have to wait for the return to be processed. If you choose to wait for your return to be processed prior to placing a new order, Avow Apparel cannot guarantee that the item you would like to order will be in stock.</p>
                                        <p>Packing the product appropriately, and attaching the shipping label correctly, is the responsibility of the customer. Avow Apparel will not be held responsible for products that are damaged as a result of insecure packaging. If damaged merchandise is received Avow Apparel will attempt to contact the customer 3 times. After 14 days (including weekends &amp; holidays) the goods will be considered abandoned and a refund will not be issued. Avow Apparel will not be held responsible for returned packages that are mislabeled and are sent back to the customer or sent to a different address. In such cases, if the customer chooses to ship the items back to us, the cost of doing so would be his/her responsibility and not that of Avow Apparel.</p>
                                        <p>Avow Apparel will not process any returns or exchanges that follow any method other than the one outlined in this Return &amp; Exchange Policy. Avow Apparel, reserves the right to refuse a return or exchange request without disclosing reasons for refusal.</p>
                                        <p><strong>US RETURNS &amp; EXCHANGES</strong></p>
                                        <p>
                                            To return an item(s) for a refund please make sure your item(s) meet the criteria mentioned in our Return &amp; Exchange Policy. We request that you package the item(s) in a secure carton or in the original packaging. When you are ready to return the item(s) please log into your Avow Apparel account, go to your order history, click on the order, and follow the prompts. A return label will be emailed to you. Please print the label, secure it onto the package, and drop it in a mailbox. You may also take it to any authorized United State Postal Service facility. Please note that you will be charged the return shipping fee (please see below chart for return shipping costs.) If you misplace your return label or accidentally delete the email containing the label, please contact us at <a href="mailto:Info@AvowApparel.com">Info@AvowApparel.com<script cf-hash="f9e31" type="text/javascript">
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               /* <![CDATA[ */!function () { try { var t = "currentScript" in document ? document.currentScript : function () { for (var t = document.getElementsByTagName("script"), e = t.length; e--;) if (t[e].getAttribute("cf-hash")) return t[e] }(); if (t && t.previousSibling) { var e, r, n, i, c = t.previousSibling, a = c.getAttribute("data-cfemail"); if (a) { for (e = "", r = parseInt(a.substr(0, 2), 16), n = 2; a.length - n; n += 2) i = parseInt(a.substr(n, 2), 16) ^ r, e += String.fromCharCode(i); e = document.createTextNode(e), c.parentNode.replaceChild(e, c) } } } catch (u) { } }();/* ]]> */</script></a> and someone will get back to you within 48 hours.
                                        </p>
